<h2>Trade Up Strategies by Tier</h2>
<p>Different rarity tiers offer different trade up opportunities. Consumer to Industrial trade ups are the cheapest but typically produce the smallest profits. Mil-Spec to Restricted trade ups are the most popular because inputs are affordable and some Restricted skins can be quite valuable. Restricted to Classified and Classified to Covert trade ups have higher stakes — both the input costs and potential returns are significantly larger.</p>

